{"tid":658291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔不願面對，習近平同金正恩在大連舉行會晤","createTime":"2018-05-09T00:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T06:08:13.000Z","uid":62646,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d20b5d3dd09ffa1e1f88407c269ce4fb71f66cc5","tid":658291,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T00:12:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2018-05/08/c_1122802575.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2Fpolitics%2F2018-05%2F08%2Fc_1122802575.htm&d=Bz9miVcwoXDXnofmbv%2BrrIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=4f5894e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2018-05/08/c_1122802575.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n金正恩表示，今年3月以來，朝中友誼和朝鮮半島形勢都取得了富有意義的進展，這是我同總書記同志歷史性會晤的積極成果。在當前地區形勢快速發展的關鍵時期，我再次來到中國同總書記見面並通報情況，希望同中方加強戰略溝通和合作，推動朝中友誼深入發展，促進地區和平穩定<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/081213_2646314ae5d234eec6040180486f5026.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F081213_2646314ae5d234eec6040180486f5026.png&h=3748aa58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7556adbc54faff7ab88fef0bc841bafd8fb3abe","tid":658291,"uid":62646,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T00:14:53.000Z","msg":"又話金仔唔show中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5af68494aefbe972d1c779c64f55a0d00d8db0","tid":658291,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T00:15:48.000Z","msg":"好明顯係比左好多著數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f14477f7f21ee676f75c83d6b2722fb7c2a4f2a","tid":658291,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T00:17:14.000Z","msg":"金仔笑到咁<img src=\"/